The trip plan has been developed to visit all 7 cities within 18 days, satisfying the given constraints and using only direct flights for commuting between cities. The stay durations were adjusted to fit the total of 18 days while meeting the critical time constraints: Frankfurt must include days 5-6 for the annual show, Mykonos must include a day between 10-12 for the meeting, and Manchester must include a day between 15-18 for the wedding. The adjusted durations are: Porto (2 days), Geneva (2 days instead of the desired 3), Mykonos (2 days instead of the desired 3), Manchester (3 days instead of the desired 4), Hamburg (4 days instead of the desired 5), Naples (3 days instead of the desired 5), and Frankfurt (2 days).

The itinerary ensures all direct flight connections are available:
- Hamburg to Frankfurt (Day 4 to Day 5)
- Frankfurt to Geneva (Day 6 to Day 7)
- Geneva to Mykonos (Day 8 to Day 9)
- Mykonos to Naples (Day 10 to Day 11)
- Naples to Manchester (Day 13 to Day 14)
- Manchester to Porto (Day 16 to Day 17)

